<varlistentry id="options.BackColor">
<term>BackColor <emphasis remap='I'>color</emphasis></term>
      <listitem>
<para>Specifies the background color associated with this style. 
<emphasis remap='I'>color</emphasis> is a color definition in one of the <ulink url="ColorScheme#color_values">color formats</ulink> supported by AfterStep.
</para><para>
BackColor is also used to calculate bevel colors used to draw a border around a widget.
</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
